Cyber Security "INTO THE AI REALM CYBER GAME PLAN REVITALIZED"
8 Nov 2023

Mr. Sutee Apichonratanakorn, Chief Executive Officer of NAT Absolute Technologies PCL, received the Top Rising Star 2023 award at the Cyber Security seminar "INTO THE AI REALM CYBER GAME PLAN REVITALIZED", the biggest event of the year organized by nforce Secure Public Company Limited on November 8, 2023.

              

nforce Secure Public Company Limited is an expert and distributor of various cyber security solution products, which are comprehensive in terms of information technology security, data management, and networking solutions. Their security operating platform includes advanced software and products for cloud and data center security, network security products, advanced threat detection, data security, system upgrades, and data analysis. They also specialize in transforming big data into security intelligence.

For more information, you can visit their website at https://www.nforcesecure.com/th

SEA Promising Cloud Partner of the Year
At the Genesys APAC Partner Conference 2023, held at the JW Marriott Phuket Resort & Spa, was captured in photos. Mr. Pheemaphol Munchukangwan, Assistant Director of Business Development and Engineering Supervisor (AVP Engineering) at Nat Consulting Co., Ltd., received the award for SEA Promising Cloud Partner of the Year.

MTECH Excellence Business Transformation
Partner Connect 2023, 20th Anniversary: Golden Era, The Gala night witnessed the prestigious recognition of Mr. Pheemaphol Munchukangwan, Assistant Director of Engineering at NAT Absolute Technologies PCL, as the recipient of the MTECH Excellence Business Transformation 2022 award. This honor was bestowed upon him during the Partner Connect 2023, 20th Anniversary: Golden Era, The Gala night held at The Athenee Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel in Bangkok. The award was presented by M Technologies (Thailand) Ltd.

NAT X NT Sales Workshop
"Open House, Open Heart, Open to New Things for NT" Power of P: Join Us, Experience a world of endless possibilities. NAT Absolute Technologies PCL and National Telecom Public Company Limited (NT) are jointly organizing an academic seminar and workshop titled "Open House, Open Heart, Open to New Things for NT" Power of P: Join Us, Experience a world of endless possibilities. This event is made possible through collaboration with our business partners, including DELL Technologies, Radware, Fortinet, Genesys, and Group-IB. The topics of discussion include "Opening Communication Solutions with Intelligent Cloud PBX and Cloud Contact Center" followed by an engaging discussion on "Shining a Light on New Threats with Real-life Experiences" along with a presentation on "Exploring New Perspectives with Design Thinking" and a workshop on Monday, July 10, 2566, at the Phra Prom Conference Room, Asawin Grand Convention Hotel, Bangkok.
More details
VMware Partner Executive Meeting
Rising Star Partner of the Year 2023, Mr. Sutee Apichanaratanakorn, Chief Executive Officer of Nat Absolute Technologies PCL, was honored with the prestigious Thailand Rising Star Partner of the Year 2023 award at Hotel Muse Bangkok. The award ceremony was organized by VMware (Thailand) Co., Ltd.
